<h1> Chocolate Chip Cookie Recipe</h1>
<h2> Cookies are Made of Butter and Love</h2>
<h3> By: Marie Sechuk ~ March 8th 2016</h3>
 

<p>
Chocolate Chip Cookies are drop cookies that feature chocolate chips.  Chocolate chip cookies originated in the United States. variations of this cookies include different types of chocolate, nuts, and oats.  </p>





